\fB\-vc \fIcores\fR, \fB\-\-vm-cores \fIcores\fR
The maximum allowed cores to be allocated to VMs at a time.
Set to \fB\-1\fR to automatically use the quota value.
Setting \fIcores\fR to \fB0\fR is equivalent to disabling the cloud.
The value for \fIcores\fR must be an integer value.
Default: -1
